attributes.review: When I downloaded this app I expected there to be feet pics of our president but sadly I was let down. Also I expected to see some exclusive content of Donald Trump visiting the kids in his basement but yet again I was let down. This app is very misleading and I do not recommend anyone to get this app. Also the app gave my phone a bunch of viruses and it kept notifying me that there were hot single middle aged moms in my area. Although that is very helpful and I will be checking up on those moms I don’t want to keep getting those notifications every 10 seconds.
